ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A comprehensive overview of the newest scholarship in the region.
I would highly recommend it. I hope other Areas' specialists have similar seminars..

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I feel that this course has made me conversant in some the most dynamic debates in South Asian studies.

Apart from what already mentioned above, 942 expands the perspectives from which I have been looking at my context of research, incites questions I had not thought of, and broadens the landscape of my academic interlocutors. On top of it, it is attended by many auditors of different years and departments, so not much pressure for young students.
